videos.headline: Evans give the Warhawks a late lead
videos.description: UL Monroe's Zach Jackson throws a quick pass to Caleb Evans for a 34-yard touchdown, giving them a 45-42 lead over Coastal Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Evans give the Warhawks a late lead) 2019/11/23 ESHEET
